T1  - Once again, is openness good for growth?
AU  - Lee, Ha Yan
AU  - Ricci, Luca Antonio
AU  - Rigobon, Roberto
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 75
IS  - 2
SP  - 451
EP  - 472
PY  - 2004
DA  - 2004/12/01/
